WEBVTT

00:02.168 --> 00:04.970
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:06.072 --> 00:07.506
     Afternoon, everybody.      

00:07.574 --> 00:08.807
              ALL:              
             Norm!              

00:08.875 --> 00:11.110
        Hey, Mr. P. How's       
         life in the big city?  

00:11.177 --> 00:13.946
     Hey, what'd I tell you     
     about those fat jokes?     

00:16.649 --> 00:18.817
    Uh, what's                  
in the box there, Norm?         

00:18.885 --> 00:20.719
    Only my brand-new           
     Turbo Flex Airmasters      

00:20.787 --> 00:22.287
    with the custom pump fit    

00:22.355 --> 00:24.289
         and the night reflector
                  racing stripe.

00:24.357 --> 00:25.624
                 Ah, whoa!      

00:25.692 --> 00:27.192
Ooh, look at that!              

00:27.260 --> 00:28.794
    Major shoe.                 

00:28.862 --> 00:31.330
            And check out the   
                 reflector, huh?

00:31.398 --> 00:34.166
      Wow, shines like          
    the Northern Lights.        

00:34.234 --> 00:35.668
                            Yep.

00:35.735 --> 00:37.569
                 Get this-- they
              utilize a patented

00:37.637 --> 00:39.204
                 ergonomic lever
              propulsion design.

00:39.272 --> 00:42.307
            Uses your body's own
Achilles tendon as a fulcrum.   

00:42.375 --> 00:43.709
        I read in <i>Runner's World</i>

00:43.777 --> 00:46.145
      that they can improve your
vertical leap by ten percent.   

00:46.212 --> 00:47.479
                  Try 12%, babe.

00:47.547 --> 00:49.214
                Ooh.            

00:49.282 --> 00:52.451
Ah, that's more than            
a shoe there, Normie,           
that's a god.                   

00:52.519 --> 00:54.353
                 And now, if you
          gentlemen will just...

00:54.421 --> 00:55.988
                      stand back
                 for a second...

00:57.924 --> 01:00.526
                ...I'm gonna try
              these puppies out.

01:03.196 --> 01:04.663
         And we're off!         

01:05.865 --> 01:07.633
      (theme song begins)       

