    ¶ Making your way           
      in the world today ¶      

01:14.174 --> 01:17.142
¶ Takes everything you've got ¶ 

01:17.210 --> 01:19.912
        ¶ Taking a break        
    from all your worries ¶     

01:19.979 --> 01:23.382
¶ Sure would help a lot ¶       

01:23.450 --> 01:26.318
      ¶ Wouldn't you like       
         to get away? ¶         

