         ¶ You wanna be         
      where you can see ¶       

01:43.737 --> 01:46.205
         ¶ Our troubles         
    are all the same ¶          

01:46.272 --> 01:50.242
      ¶ You wanna be where      
  everybody knows your name ¶   

01:51.678 --> 01:54.179
         ¶ You wanna go         
      where people know ¶       

